            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-01-06T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-06-22T18:00:00-05:00" n="596" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d596">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>China aid legislation was approved as Section 12 of Public Law 47 on April 19; 63
                    Stat. 50, 55. It made available to the President through February 15, 1950, an
                    amount equal to the unobligated balance of funds appropriated by Public Law 793
                    of 1948 “for assistance in areas in China which he may deem to be not under
                    Communist domination”.</p>
            </div>
